1. *Gotov* sam da krenem. (I'm ready to go.)
2. *Gotova* je večera. (The dinner is ready.)
3. *Gotovi* smo. (We are done.)
4. *Gotovina* je potrebna za kupovinu. (Cash is needed for purchase.)
5. *Gotovom* obliku može da se pristupi. (The finished form can be accessed.)
6. *Gotove* stvari su spremne za upotrebu. (The finished items are ready for use.)